      "span_text": "A recent study of the incidence and prevalence of CP in Olmstead County, USA, made use of unusual arrangements for the provision of medical care in its methodology.  In this US county, nearly all medical care is provided by a central hospital (renowned for keeping large longitudinal databases of patient records) and a single primary care centre."
